<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">The Chinese Injured and Disabled People Sports Association</ENAMEX> -LRB- renamed to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Chinese Disabled Sports Association</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1990</ENAMEX> -RRB- was established in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">October , 1983</ENAMEX> .
