<ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">Since 1984</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the Chinese Disabled Sports Association</ENAMEX> has become a member of <ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">8</ENAMEX> international disabled sports organizations successively , such as <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the International Para Olympic Committee</ENAMEX> , etc. and has established relations with disabled sports organizations in various countries and areas and taken part in international events such as <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">the Special Olympic Games</ENAMEX> , etc .
