<ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">" The Guaranteed Law for Disabled Persons in the People 's Republic of China "</ENAMEX> , which was drafted and implemented in <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">1991</ENAMEX> , stipulates to organize and support disabled people to develop mass sports activities , to hold special games and to participate in important international competitions and communication .
